Program: Outlook
Title: Paralympics Special
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00xm82d
Last Broadcast Date: Sat 1 Sep 2012
Outlook celebrates the start of the Paralympic Games with an hour-long programme live from the heart of the action. Matthew Bannister hears the extraordinary personal stories of disabled athletes from around the world who have come to London to compete or remember past achievements, as well as those with a special connection to the Games. Show less